            a.blogs-showblogsentryheadline(href='http://www.unknown-horizons.org/unknown-horizons-release-2013-3/', title='Unknown Horizons Release 2013.3') Unknown Horizons Release 2013.3
            .blogs-showblogsentrytime-author-wrapper
              | Posted at: Oct 10, 2013 by
              | Chris Oelmueller
              br
              | Categorized under:   Â»Releases
            .CGBlogSummaryContent
              p Hey everyone!
              p
                | Time for a new release:
                em Unknown Horizons 2013.3
                | has been tagged and packaged!
              p New features in this release:
              ul
                li New disaster: the plague aka "the black death"
                li The doctor is back and is now needed to cure the black death
                li Medical herbs can now be produced for the doctor
                li Hotkeys can now be set in the settings
                li Many user-interface improvements
                li Fixed some bad bugs causing the game to crash completely
                li Lots of small improvements
              p
                a(href='https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/blob/2013.3/doc/CHANGELOG.md')
                  | Our
                  strong changelog
                | contains more details about crashes and other bugs that we fixed.
              p
                a(title='Screenshot: The plague', href='uploads/images/uh-release-2013.3/2013-07-02.23-28-28.105588.png', target='_blank')
                  img(title='The Plague', src='uploads/images/uh-release-2013.3/2013-07-02.23-28-28.105588.png', alt='The plague haunts the city!', width='341', height='256')
                  br
                  | The plague haunts the city.
              p
                a(title='Screenshot: The hotkey settings', href='uploads/images/uh-release-2013.3/2013_3-hotkeys-3.png', target='_blank')
                  img(title='Hotkey Settings', src='uploads/images/uh-release-2013.3/2013_3-hotkeys-3.png', alt='The new hotkey settings view', width='455', height='166')
                  br
                  | The new hotkey settings menu
              p
                | All in all, the combination of Unknown Horizons 2013.3 and FIFE 0.3.5 is intended to provide a far more stable gaming experience. If you do spot a bug or notice odd behavior however, please let us know at
                a(title='Unknown Horizons Bug Tracker', href='http://bugs.unknown-horizons.org') http://bugs.unknown-horizons.org
                | .
              h3 Get Involved
              p
                | Interested in helping with the development of
                em Unknown Horizons
                | ? Great, we are looking for help in all areas. Everyone can help! Check out our
                strong
                  a(href='get-involved/') Get Involved
                | page and get in touch with the team, we are awaiting you.
              h3 Downloads
              p
                | Enough with the paperwork -
                strong
                  a(href='download/') Get Unknown Horizons 2013.3
                  | ,
                | have fun and
                a(href='forum/') let us know what you think
                | !
                br
                | Your
                em
                  a(href='https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/blob/master/doc/AUTHORS.md') Unknown Horizons Team
            br
