            a.blogs-showblogsentryheadline(href='http://www.unknown-horizons.org/devblog/106/114/Development-update/', title='Development update') Development update
            .blogs-showblogsentrytime-author-wrapper
              | Posted at: Aug 26, 2013 by
              | stubb
              br
              | Categorized under:   Â»Main Development
            .CGBlogSummaryContent
              div Hey everyone,
              div this is another short update on the current state of development.
              br
              h3 FIFE Release
              div
                | Our friends from FIFE released a new version
                a(href='http://blog.fifengine.net/2013/08/22/fife-0-3-5-released/') (0.3.5)
                | of their engine. It is a minor bug fix release which fixes some crashes related to Unknown Horizons, hopefully improving your game experience.
              br
              h3 Our plans
              div
                | As some of you have probably already noticed we modified our milestones at Github again. The current plan is a new release of Unknown Horizons in the beginning of October. The release will based on the FIFE release 0.3.5 mentioned above and include some of the nice features we introduced within the last blog posts, animated overlays for example.
              br
              h3 Call for translations
              div
                | There are a few weeks left until the release. Enough to (re-)check if the translation into your native language is already complete or needs some love. You can find our translation server at
                a(href='http://translate.unknown-horizons.org') http://translate.unknown-horizons.org
                | .
              br
              div All the best,
              div
                em The Unknown Horizons Team
            br
