            a.blogs-showblogsentryheadline(href='http://www.unknown-horizons.org/devblog/105/114/We-need-you/', title='We need you! ') We need you!
            .blogs-showblogsentrytime-author-wrapper
              | Posted at: Aug 13, 2013 by
              | Nihathrael
              br
              | Categorized under:   Â»Main Development
            .CGBlogSummaryContent
              div Hey everyone,
              div
                | this is a very short news update on the current state. Development is currently moving along at a somewhat slow speed, as everyone is quite busy with important real-life tasks, but we are moving forward.
              br
              h3 We need YOU!
              div
                | Have you ever wanted to work on a game project and make your visions come true? Are you eager to work on a complex python codebase, create splendid graphics or design the mechanics of a game enjoyed by thousands of players every year?
              div
                | If you answered some or all of those questions with "YES, I do!",
                strong
                  | contact us on
                  a(href='support/irc/') IRC
                  | or
                  a(href='mailto:team@unknown-horizons.org') mail
                | . We can offer some great experience, interesting challenges and hope to meet you soon!
              br
              h3 Release
              div
                | We are eagerly awaiting the release of FIFE 0.3.5, as it contains a lot of bugfixes, that we need in order to deliver a stable version 2013.3. We expect the FIFE release in the coming week or two, so you should hear more about our next release soon.
              br
              div All the best,
              div
                em The Unknown Horizons Team
